Or if you don't mind brewing up your own rustproofing concoction, here's 
a homemade recipe for Waxoyl: 
http://www.geocities.com/wallaces_21/waxoyl.html

Waxoyl is a commercial rustproofing product that's popular with the 
British car crowd, e.g.: http://www.robisonservice.com/servicedep/waxoyl.asp

